        </tr>
        <tr class="even">
          <td>Name</td>
          <td>Shows the name of a preference for an NVT.</td>
        </tr>
        <tr class="odd">
          <td>Value</td>
          <td>Shows current value of a preference for an NVT.</td>
        </tr>
